Short:	 	HD Installer for Slightly Magic v1.0b
Author:		Keith Krellwitz (abaddon@wwa.com)
Uploader:	Keith Krellwitz (abaddon@wwa.com)
Type:	 	game/patch

This installer requires the original Slightly Magic disk by the Code
Masters.

- Requires JST!

The HD-Patched game will need 2.0 megs of memory.

It has been successfully tested on a A1200/030/40MHz/10MB and on a
A2000/040/28MHz/17MB.

At anytime press 'F10' to quit back to workbench.

More than likely you'll have to set the NOCACHES tooltype for this one.

This loader uses the JOTD HDstartup written by Jean-Francois Fabre.

